\newlabel{fig:headline}{{1}{2}{Task completion (pass@1) averaged across all domains. GPT-5 (reasoning) achieves 85\%. Voice agents show two levels of degradation: under \textbf {Clean} conditions (clean audio, no interruptions), performance drops to 31--51\% ($-$34 to $-$54pp); under \textbf {Realistic} conditions (realistic audio, interruptions), it falls further to 25--38\% ($-$47 to $-$59pp from text).\revised {Was 80\%, 29--42\% ($-$38 to $-$51pp), 19--30\% ($-$50 to $-$61pp).}}{figure.caption.1}{}}
